        "function": {
            "name": "activate_sdk_template_management_tools",
            "description": "Call this tool when you need access to a new category of tools. The category of tools is described as follows:\n\nThis group of tools is focused on managing SDK templates specifically for the Prolog environment within the Teatro framework. The tools allow users to retrieve and list available SDK templates, as well as access the content of specific templates. By utilizing these tools, developers can efficiently browse through a catalog of templates, ensuring they have the necessary resources to build and customize their applications effectively. The ability to get the content of a specific SDK template enables users to understand the structure and components of the templates they are working with, facilitating better integration and usage in their projects.\n\nBe sure to call this tool if you need a capability related to the above."
        },
        "type": "function"
