##  7.  [Navigate to header](https://modelcontextprotocol.io/specification/2025-06-18/server/resources#error-handling) Error Handling

Servers SHOULD return standard JSON-RPC errors for common failure cases:
Resource not found: `-32002`
Internal errors: `-32603`

Example error:   [Image: Image]


```
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "error": {
    "code": -32002,
    "message": "Resource not found",
    "data": {
      "uri": "file:///nonexistent.txt"
    }
  }
}

```

